description: Vanadian Energy Corp. focuses on exploration of vanadium deposits in Canada. The company holds 100% interests in the Pipewrench Lake and Narrows Lake properties consisting of three claim blocks located in Saskatchewan; and 25% interest in the Clearwater project located in northern Saskatchewan. It also holds interests in the Huzyk Creek Vanadium property that consists of approximately 216 square kilometers mineral exploration license located in north-central Manitoba. The company was formerly known as Uracan Resources Ltd. and changed its name to Vanadian Energy Corp. in October 2018. Vanadian Energy Corp. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
